main(role='main')
  section.jumbotron.text-center
    .container
      img#artistCoverImage
      h1.jumbotron-heading {{artistName}}
      p.lead.text-muted
        | Something short and leading about the collection belowâ€”its contents, the creator, etc. Make it short and sweet, but not too short so folks don't simply skip over it entirely.
      p
        a.btn.btn-primary.my-2(href='#') Shuffle Play
        a.btn.btn-secondary.my-2(href='#') Start Radio
  .album.py-5.bg-light
    .container
      .row
        .col-md-4(ng-repeat='album in albums')
          .card.mb-4.box-shadow
            img.card-img-top(alt='Thumbnail [100%x225]', style='height: 225px; width: 100%; display: block;', src='{{album.artUrl}}', data-holder-rendered='true')
            .card-body
              p.card-text
                | {{album.name}}
              .d-flex.justify-content-between.align-items-center
                .btn-group
                  button.btn.btn-sm.btn-outline-secondary(type='button') Songs: {{album.songCount}}
                  button.btn.btn-sm.btn-outline-secondary(type='button') Plays: {{album.playCount}}
                small.text-muted {{album.year}}  
.container
    .row
    table#tracksTable.row-border.hover(datatable='ng', dt-options='dtOptions', style="min-height:500px;")
        thead
            th.hidden id
            th Title
        tbody
            tr(ng-repeat='track in tracks')
                td.hidden {{ track.id }}
                td {{ track.title }}
    
        